{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 47,
  "title": "第四十七章（鑑遠）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "不出戶知天下，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不窺牖見天道，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其出彌遠，其知彌少。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人不行而知，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不見而名，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不為而成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不出戶以知天下者，以己身知人身，以己家知人家，所以見天下也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天道與人道同，天人相通，精氣相貫。人君清淨，天氣自正，人君多欲，天氣煩濁。吉兇利害，皆由於己。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂去其家觀人家，去其身觀人身，所觀益遠，所見益少也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人不上天，不入淵，能知天下者，以心知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上好道，下好德；上好武，下好力。聖人原小知大，察內知外。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上無所為，則下無事，家給人足，萬物自化就也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
